---
import Layout from '../../layouts/layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="SentinelOne Security Solutions">

<main class="bg-gray-900 text-white min-h-screen">

<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-24">

<div class="flex items-center gap-6">

<img src="/logos/sentinelone.png" class="h-12">

<div>

<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-400">
SentinelOne
</h1>

<p class="text-gray-300 mt-2">
AI-powered autonomous cybersecurity platform for endpoint, cloud, and identity protection.
</p>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 pb-24 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">
Core Products
</h2>

<ul class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-2">

<li>• Singularity XDR</li>
<li>• Singularity EDR</li>
<li>• Cloud Security Platform</li>
<li>• Identity Threat Detection</li>

</ul>

</div>

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">
Capabilities
</h2>

<ul class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-2">

<li>• AI-driven threat detection</li>
<li>• Automated incident response</li>
<li>• Ransomware protection</li>
<li>• Endpoint visibility and control</li>

</ul>

</div>

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">
Use Cases
</h2>

<ul class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-2">

<li>• Endpoint protection for enterprises</li>
<li>• Threat hunting and SOC operations</li>
<li>• Ransomware defense</li>
<li>• Cloud workload protection</li>

</ul>

</div>

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">
Why SentinelOne
</h2>

<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-300">
SentinelOne provides autonomous endpoint security powered by artificial intelligence,
enabling organizations to detect, respond, and remediate threats without human intervention.
</p>

</div>

</section>

</main>

</Layout>
